text: Assemini (Assèmini) is a town and comune (municipality) in the Metropolitan City of Cagliari in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 26,818 people lived there. Its area is 118.17 km². It is 6 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == * Category:Communes of the Metropolitan City of Cagliari
